{"word":"κυδάνω","slug":"κυδάνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κυδάνω</b></el> <el>(κῡδάνω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:κυδαίνω'><el>κυδαίνω</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> and <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a>,\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to hold in honour</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to vaunt, boast</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}